From c852d2abee30f464cbf08369e985219fe850dd0f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ping-Ke Shih <pkshih@realtek.com>
Date: Mon, 17 Feb 2025 14:30:53 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: rtw89: add H2C command of TX time for WiFi 7 chips
Git-commit: c852d2abee30f464cbf08369e985219fe850dd0f
Patch-mainline: v6.15-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

BT-coexistence configure WiFi TX time to share time slots with Bluetooth
devices. Since the format is different from WiFi 6 chips, add the new
format accordingly.

Signed-off-by: Ping-Ke Shih <pkshih@realtek.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250217063053.38936-3-pkshih@realtek.com
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

